name: Encounter with life
description:
Sometimes we find ourselves lost in our own lives, with so much going on around us, but we seem to be incapable. Work, responsibility, pressure, it's a bunch of things that make us think "where did I stop?", "Where did I get lost?". Life seems to play with us in some hypotheses, in order to prove to us something we can't see.
This piece was created with the aim of showing a disconnection, a moment of peace, away from everything and everyone, moving away from life to find your own life. Sometimes it's best to let go of everything and find ourselves.

_____
